						               													<description>Fruit Punch is a fruit-themed game where players have to collect Fruit cards to win the game. The deck contains 62 cards, which consist of Fruit and Animal cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In the beginning, each player is given 5 Fruit cards. The players take turns drawing card(s) from the draw pile until someone draws Mad Monkey. When that happens, the player is knocked out. However, the knocked-out player can still take action and gather points.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;During their turn, players may either play a fruit card as an Action card or place it in their Field as a Point card. To end the turn, the player must draw at least 1 card from the pile. If the drawn card is an Animal, the player must end the turn and get the penalty written on the card. The game continues clockwise until only 1 player left, and the player with the most points wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
